    <h1>TeaTime - README</h1>
    
    <h2>Store Name</h2>
    <p>TeaTime</p>
    
    <h2>What are you selling?</h2>
    <p>We are selling a variety of teas from around the world, including black teas, green teas, herbal teas, and custom tea blends.</p>
    
    <h2>Additional Pages and How to Operate Them</h2>
    <p>We added the following additional pages:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Quiz:</strong> 
            <p>A interactive quiz that helps users find their perfect tea based on their preferences.</p>
            <p>To use: Navigate to /store/quiz, answer the questions about your tea preferences, click on "Find My Tea", and receive a personalized tea recommendation.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Blender:</strong> 
            <p>A custom tea blending tool where users can create their own unique tea blends.</p>
            <p>To use: Go to /store/tea-blender, select a base tea, add flavors using the sliders, name your blend, and click "Create Blend" to save it to your account.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Map:</strong> 
            <p>An interactive map showing the origins of our teas.</p>
            <p>To use: Visit /store/map, explore the interactive world map, click on markers to see a list of teas from different regions.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Reviews:</strong> 
            <p>A page where customers can leave and view product reviews.</p>
            <p>To use: Navigate to /store/reviews, read existing reviews, or click "Add a Review" to submit your own review</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
    
    <h2>What was hard to do?</h2>
    <p>Some of the challenging aspects of this project included:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Implementing the custom tea blender functionality with real-time updates and visualization using Chart.js.</li>
        <li>Setting up the admin panel with user activity tracking and product management, ensuring proper access control.</li>
        <li>Developing the search functionality for the admin page, allowing filtering of user activities based on username prefixes.</li>
        <li>Integrating custom tea blends with regular product functions, ensuring they can be added to the cart, checked out, and managed similarly to standard products.</li>
    </ul>
    
